&lt;h4&gt;The Company:&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;isSelectedEnd&quot;&gt;Placements AI is building the operating system for advertising. As a product-first company, we are transforming the way digital media publishers, broadcasters, retail media networks, and eCommerce businesses manage their advertising operations through AI-powered technology and automation.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;isSelectedEnd&quot;&gt;Our platform streamlines advertising sales, operations, billing, and revenue reporting, enabling customers to scale efficiently and drive greater business outcomes. We believe in creating a connected ecosystem that helps our customers modernize and simplify the complexities of advertising operations.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Headquartered in New York City, Placements AI has a global footprint with offices in Seattle, London, Taipei, and Denver, as well as the APAC region.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;&quot; data-start=&quot;601&quot; data-end=&quot;1035&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;601&quot; data-end=&quot;617&quot;&gt;The Position:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;&quot; data-start=&quot;601&quot; data-end=&quot;1035&quot;&gt;&lt;br data-start=&quot;617&quot; data-end=&quot;620&quot;&gt;We are looking for a Intermediate Backend Engineer to join our growing engineering team in Taipei. In this hybrid role (three days per week in office), you will be a key contributor to the design, development, and maintenance of our advertising technology platform. You’ll work alongside a talented team and collaborate cross-functionally to deliver high-quality, scalable solutions that support our clients’ evolving needs.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;&quot; data-start=&quot;1037&quot; data-end=&quot;1354&quot;&gt;Placements.io continues to invest in platform innovation, including the integration of AI-driven features to enhance automation, predictive insights, and reporting performance. If you&#39;re passionate about backend development and excited about shaping the future of AdTech—including AI-driven automation and robust external integrations—this is an excellent opportunity.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;p-rich_text_section&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our tech stack includes&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ruby on Rails&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;PostgresSQL&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Elastic search&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Engineering team tackles a wide range of challenges—from big data and system scalability to improving user experience. You’ll have opportunities to work across the stack or specialize deeply in backend systems and integrations.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;p-rich_text_section&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong data-stringify-type=&quot;bold&quot;&gt;Key Responsibilities:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;ul class=&quot;p-rich_text_list p-rich_text_list__bullet&quot; data-stringify-type=&quot;unordered-list&quot; data-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;&quot; data-start=&quot;1688&quot; data-end=&quot;1763&quot;&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;&quot; data-start=&quot;1690&quot; data-end=&quot;1763&quot;&gt;Design, build, and maintain robust, scalable APIs and backend services.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;&quot; data-start=&quot;1764&quot; data-end=&quot;1863&quot;&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;&quot; data-start=&quot;1766&quot; data-end=&quot;1863&quot;&gt;Collaborate with product managers, designers, and engineers to define technical specifications.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;&quot; data-start=&quot;1864&quot; data-end=&quot;1980&quot;&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;&quot; data-start=&quot;1866&quot; data-end=&quot;1980&quot;&gt;Implement backend logic to support AI-enhanced features like automated workflows and intelligent data reporting.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;&quot; data-start=&quot;1981&quot; data-end=&quot;2046&quot;&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;&quot; data-start=&quot;1983&quot; data-end=&quot;2046&quot;&gt;Optimize system performance and resolve bottleneck

&lt;h4&gt;The Company:&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;isSelectedEnd&quot;&gt;Placements AI is building the operating system for advertising. As a product-first company, we are transforming the way digital media publishers, broadcasters, retail media networks, and eCommerce businesses manage their advertising operations through AI-powered technology and automation.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;isSelectedEnd&quot;&gt;Our platform streamlines advertising sales, operations, billing, and revenue reporting, enabling customers to scale efficiently and drive greater business outcomes. We believe in creating a connected ecosystem that helps our customers modernize and simplify the complexities of advertising operations.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Headquartered in New York City, Placements AI has a global footprint with offices in Seattle, London, Taipei, and Denver, as well as the APAC region.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;&quot; data-start=&quot;601&quot; data-end=&quot;1035&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;601&quot; data-end=&quot;617&quot;&gt;The Position:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We&#39;re looking for a Quality Assurance Engineer to help ensure the reliability, performance, and quality of our products as we continue to scale globally.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a QA Engineer, you&#39;ll work closely with Product Managers, Engineers, and Designers to validate new features, identify defects before they reach customers, and help drive a culture of quality throughout the software development lifecycle. You&#39;ll play a critical role in ensuring our platform delivers an exceptional experience for customers around the world.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role is hybrid, with three days per week based in our Taipei office.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;p-rich_text_section&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong data-stringify-type=&quot;bold&quot;&gt;Key Responsibilities:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Design, develop, and execute test plans, test cases, and test scenarios for new and existing features&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Perform manual, exploratory, functional, regression, and end-to-end testing across web applications and APIs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify, document, prioritize, and track software defects through resolution&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate closely with Product Managers, Engineers, and Designers to understand requirements and ensure quality standards are met&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Validate bug fixes and perform regression testing before releases&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with engineers to improve test coverage and quality throughout the development lifecycle&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist in building, maintaining, and enhancing automated test suites&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Analyze application performance, usability, and reliability issues&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Participate in sprint planning, backlog grooming, and release processes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Advocate for quality assurance best practices and continuous improvement initiatives&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;p-rich_text_section&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-stringify-type=&quot;bold&quot;&gt;Qualifications:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;5+ years of experience in Software Quality Assurance, Quality Engineering, or a related field&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong understanding of software testing methodologies, QA processes, and testing best practices&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience testing web applications and APIs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience creating and executing detailed test plans and test cases&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Familiarity with defect tracking and project management tools such as Jira&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong analytical, troubleshooting, and problem-solving skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience working in Agile development environments&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent communication and collaboration skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to manage multiple priorities in a fast-paced environment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
